               <p>I live in <placeName id="t17891028-40-crimeloc194">Upper Newman-street, at the sign of the City of Hereford, a publick house</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17891028-40-crimeloc194" type="placeName" value="Upper Newman-street, at the sign of the City of Hereford, a publick house"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17891028-40-crimeloc194" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891028-40-off192 t17891028-40-crimeloc194"></join>; this robbery was between eight and nine at night, before I went to bed; my servant, Agathy Jones, missed some things, a looking-glass, a coat, and a petticoat, and a slider, which I knew; I missed them out of my bed room; I saw the glass about three o'clock; I saw the things advertised the next day; and I saw them at Litchfield-street; they are mine.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17891028-40-person435">
